(a) Gilbert, J. C.; Weerasooriya, U. Elaboration of Aldehydes and Ketones to Alkynes: Improved Methodology. J. Org. Chem. 1979, 44, 4997-4998. DOI: 10.1021/jo00394a063; (b) Gilbert, J. C.; Weerasooriya, U. Diazoethenes: Their Attempted Synthesis from Aldehydes and Aromatic Ketones by Way of the Horner-Emmons Modification of the Wittig Reaction. A Facile Synthesis of Alkynes. J. Org. Chem. 1982, 47, 1837-1845. DOI: 10.1021/jo00349a007.&#160;&#x21a9;&#xfe0e;
